title: on_exit()
brief: Called when the client exits.
seealso: on_key, on_idle, on_read_message
----

<p>If you define the function <span class="tt">on_exit</span> it will be called when the client is terminated.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
function on_exit()
   print("on_exit() called");
end
</pre>